#message:00:027
{
	[Style Right]
	[CustomVoice soundIDs=0x38C,0x0][Volume percent=96]Wassup? [Pause 5]I'm a drummer.[BR]
	[Pause 5]The parade we had a week ago[BR]
	was a lot of fun for me.[BR]
	[Pause 5]Got to flex my skills.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I dunno when the next one will be,[BR]
	but I don't think it's all that[BR]
	necessary to be honest.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Roy Al T. is a good bud of mine.[BR]
	You seen him 'round the [SaveColor][Color:09]Love Hotel[RestoreColor],[BR]
	yeah?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	We went to music school, actually.[BR]
	Passed with flying colours.[BR]
	Maybe I should pay him a visit.[BR][Wait][End]
}

#message:00:028
{
	[Style Right]
	Ah I haven't seen your face, but[BR]
	I can tell you've done very good[BR]
	things for the [SaveColor][Color:02]Sunshine Funshine[BR]
	Mafia[RestoreColor].[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I need to keep my cover while I[BR]
	kill some fools.[BR]
	[Pause 12]If I don't,[Pause 2] I may never be able to[BR]
	fulfill my bounty.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Don't snitch.[BR]
	[Pause 10]We don't like snitches.[BR][Wait][End]
}

#message:00:029
{
	[Style Right]
	Welcome to [SaveColor][Color:09]Doki Doki Castle[RestoreColor].[BR]
	[Pause 3]I'm a pastor here.[BR]
	Can I help you with anything?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Princess Peach?[BR]
	[Pause 20]She's lounging in her room today.[BR]
	I'd say don't bother her, but you[BR]
	probably won't listen to me.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Do as you please.[BR]
	[Pause 5]You[Wave] did[/fx] save our cathedral after all.[Wait][End]
}

#message:00:02A
{
	[Style Right]
	I miss my wife, Mario.[BR]
	I miss her a lot.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Praying at the cathedral won't[BR]
	bring her back, I know.[BR]
	[Pause 12]One can hope and dream, ya know...[Wait][End]
}

#message:00:02B
{
	[Style Right]
	I'm very disappointed in my wife.[BR]
	[Pause 9]She bought our son shovelware for[BR]
	his birthday![BR]
	[Pause 10][PrintRising]What kind of gift is that?[/fx][BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I realize he doesn't know any[BR]
	better,[Pause 5] but he definitely deserves[BR]
	to play [SaveColor][Color:20]actual[RestoreColor] video games.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Then I realize that all the [Rainbow]AAA[/fx][BR]
	games nowadays are overpriced[BR]
	and not worth the yen.[BR]
	[Pause 5]A lose-lose situation.[BR][Wait][End]
}

#message:00:02C
{
	[Style Right]
	This just in.[BR]
	[Pause 12]Local bean man blocks all owners[BR]
	of the Nintendo Switch 2[Size 6]TM[Size 16].[BR]
	Talk about petty.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I got one for a pretty penny off[BR]
	of [SaveColor][Color:40]eGadd[RestoreColor]. [Pause 5]Decently cheap from a[BR]
	third-party seller.[BR]
	He was very nice to me.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	With the way the economy is going,[BR]
	I'm going to pray to the Goddess[BR]
	that I can afford my bills in the[BR]
	upcoming winter.[BR][Wait][End]
}

#message:00:02D
{
	[Style Right]
	My bestie has been dying to meet[BR]
	the princess of [SaveColor][Color:09]Doki Doki Castle[RestoreColor].[BR]
	I think she has a crush on her.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	They say "don't meet your heroes",[BR]
	but maybe this can be an exception.[BR]
	[Pause 10]No harm, no foul, right?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Sure,[Pause 3] she's gorgeous and everything,[Pause 5][BR]
	but I think I'm falling for one of[BR]
	the nearby guards.[BR]
	[Pause 15]He's so shy.[Pause 5] How adorable.[BR][Wait][End]
}

#message:00:02E
{
	[Style Right]
	Sigh, I really didn't wanna come[BR]
	into work today.[BR]
	[Pause 10]My day be so fine and then,[Pause 10] [Shake]boom![/fx][BR]
	[SaveColor][Color:09]Doki Doki Castle[RestoreColor] is back.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Employment insurance was putting[BR]
	in some real effort.[BR]
	[Pause 10]Now I actually have to do stuff?[BR]
	[Pause 15]Jeez...[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	At least the sisters are cute.[BR]
	I'll do anything for them.[BR][Wait][End]
}

#message:00:02F
{
	[Style Right]
