	[Pause 5][Wave]That'd have been baaaaad.[/fx][Wait][End]
}

#message:00:030
{
	[Style Right]
	Dobrry den' to you, my friend.[BR]
	[Pause 10]Ah, pardon. It is way of greeting[BR]
	in [SaveColor][Color:0D]Land of Shiver[RestoreColor], you see.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	When in cell, I was scared. [BR]
	Strashnyy.[BR]
	[Pause 15]Ever grateful, I am, to be free[BR]
