#message:00:037
{
	[Style Right]
	Dang, I miss when Bower was in[BR]
	charge.[Pause 2] It was actually cool.[BR]
	[Pause 10]He had hookers and cookies.[BR]
	[Pause 20]Now there's just cookies.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	No hookers.[Pause 3] How lame.[BR]
	[Pause 10]No casino either.[Pause 3] Double lame.[BR]
	[Pause 10]At least Princess Peach is cute.[BR]
	Might ask her out... or not.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
