}

#message:00:038
{
	[Style Right]
	[PrintRising]Bogus! Absolute bogus![BR]
	[Pause 15]These stupid game companies think[BR]
	this is funny?[/fx][BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I went to my local games store[BR]
	and bought the next shooter.[BR]
	[Pause 15]I went to put the disc in my[BR]
	console and...[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[PrintRising][Speed delay=3 chars=1]OH WAIT![BR]
	[Pause 10][Speed delay=1 chars=1]There is no disc drive slot on my[BR]
	dang console![/fx][BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Great, so now they're practically[BR]
	writing out physical media.[BR]
	[Pause 15]I don't have good internet.[BR]
	I live in a backwater village.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	What do you want me to do?[BR]
	[Pause 10][PrintRising]DOWNLOAD the games?[/fx][BR]
	[Pause 10]What the heck is up with that?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Sheesh. Being a gamer sucks.[BR]
	I should get back into watching[BR]
	movies instead.[BR]
	[Pause 15]Huh, wait.[Pause 5] [PrintRising]Those are digital too![/fx][BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[SizeWave]Gooooollllyyy![/fx][BR]
	[Pause 10]I'm about to burst.[Wait][End]
}

